Despite all my angst, I had a wonderful Christmas. It turns out I’m the queen of charades – and now here we are heading into a whole new year, a whole new decade, my sixth on the planet … even though I’m only in my 40s. Yes, truly: anyone born between 1970 and 1979 is entering their sixth decade. Terrifying. So, time to make a new year’s resolution perhaps? I have long resolved to never make a resolution again. Whoever succeeds at these things? It’s tough to give up sugar or fags or booze or go to bed early or...